## Overview

The Email Notification System provides a robust, asynchronous email notification service for the Source Intelligence application. It supports both generic email notifications and specialized data extraction notifications with comprehensive error handling and retry mechanisms.

### Key Features
- ✅ Synchronous and asynchronous email sending
- ✅ HTML and plain text email support
- ✅ CC/BCC support
- ✅ File attachments
- ✅ Custom metadata support
- ✅ Data extraction result notifications
- ✅ Retry mechanism with exponential backoff
- ✅ Comprehensive error handling and logging

