### Example 4: Java Service Usage

```java
@Service
public class MyService {
    
    @Autowired
    private NotificationService notificationService;
    
    public void sendWelcomeEmail(String userEmail) {
        EmailNotificationDTO emailDTO = EmailNotificationDTO.builder()
            .to(List.of(userEmail))
            .subject("Welcome to Source Intelligence")
            .body("<h1>Welcome!</h1><p>Thank you for joining us.</p>")
            .htmlContent(true)
            .metadata(Map.of("type", "welcome", "userId", "123"))
            .build();
        
        NotificationRequestDTO request = NotificationRequestDTO.builder()
            .notificationType(NotificationType.EMAIL)
            .async(true)
            .emailNotification(emailDTO)
            .build();
        
        NotificationResponseDTO response = notificationService.sendNotification(request);
        log.info("Email sent: {}", response.getNotificationId());
    }
}
```

