## Deployment

### Prerequisites

- Java 17+
- Maven 3.8+
- SMTP server access (Gmail, SendGrid, etc.)
- MongoDB (for main application)

### Build

```bash
mvn clean package -DskipTests
```

### Run Locally

```bash
export EMAIL_USERNAME=your-email@gmail.com
export EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-password
mvn spring-boot:run
```

### Docker Deployment

```dockerfile
FROM openjdk:17-jdk-slim
COPY target/sourceintelligence-service.jar app.jar
ENV EMAIL_USERNAME=${EMAIL_USERNAME}
ENV EMAIL_PASSWORD=${EMAIL_PASSWORD}
ENTRYPOINT ["java", "-jar", "/app.jar"]
```

Build and run:
```bash
docker build -t si-notification-service .
docker run -p 8080:8080 \
  -e EMAIL_USERNAME=your-email \
  -e EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-password \
  si-notification-service
```

### Kubernetes Deployment

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: notification-service
spec:
  replicas: 3
  template:
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: app
        image: si-notification-service:latest
        env:
        - name: EMAIL_USERNAME
          valueFrom:
            secretKeyRef:
              name: email-credentials
              key: username
        - name: EMAIL_PASSWORD
          valueFrom:
            secretKeyRef:
              name: email-credentials
              key: password
```

